data.description: Just Listed! 16625 SW 101 Ave, Miami, Florida 33157. 3 Bedrooms, 2.5 Baths, 1630 sq ft of floorspace. 2 Parking Spaces, Car port, Impact resistant doors and windows, New Roof, New A/C, Screened-in Terrace, Covered BBQ area, Sprinklers, and Patio shed.  Gas on-demand water heater, Gas oven and stove, City gas. This stunning detached home is now available for sale! With spacious rooms and modern finishes, this property offers the perfect blend of style and comfort. Located in a desirable neighborhood, it's the ideal place to call home. Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity! Reach out to our agent today for more information or to schedule a showing.#ForSale CTA: Interested? Send us a DM now!
